#### æ ¸å¿ƒç«¯ç‚¹ï¼š`/v1/audio/speech`

**è¯·æ±‚ç¤ºä¾‹**ï¼š

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8003/v1/audio/speech \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "model": "step-audio-editx",
    "voice": "happy_en",
    "input": "Hello! This is a test.",
    "response_format": "wav",
    "step_audio": {
      "mode": "clone",
      "model_variant": "base",
      "intensity": 1.0
